== 退役舰船 ==
=== 无惧级巡逻艇 ===

{{le|无惧级巡逻艇|Fearless-class patrol vessel}}由新加坡自行制造，以替代原来老旧的巡逻艇，替换下来的巡逻艇装备于海岸警卫队。最初的6艘该级战舰以反潜作战为主要任务，隶属于第189中队。2003年1月，勇敢号在新加坡海峡与一艘集装箱货船发生了碰撞。<ref>{{cite news | title=One dead in naval collision | date=2003-01-04 | publisher=BBC | url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/2626959.stm | accessdate=2007-05-29 | archive-date=2010-04-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100401010231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/asia-pacific/2626959.stm | dead-url=no }}</ref> 2005年，第189中队转由海岸指挥部指挥，而该级12艘船转属182中队。<ref>{{cite web | title=COSCOM Expands | work=Navy News, Issue 01 2005 | url=http://www.mindef.gov.sg/navy/navynews/documents/2005/0501.pdf | accessdate=2005-03-17 | archive-date=2013-05-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130520083235/http://www.mindef.gov.sg/navy/navynews/documents/2005/0501.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref> 2020年12月11日，最后两艘无惧级巡逻艇在大士海军基地退役<ref>{{cite web | title=Final Two Patrol Vessels RSS Freedom and RSS Gallant Retire After Decades of Distinguished Service | website=MINDEF | url=https://www.mindef.gov.sg/web/portal/mindef/news-and-events/latest-releases/article-detail/2020/December/11dec20_nr | accessdate=2020-12-11 | deadurl=no | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201211141213/https://www.mindef.gov.sg/web/portal/mindef/news-and-events/latest-releases/article-detail/2020/December/11dec20_nr | archivedate=2012-12-11 }}</ref>。

